channel.title: Comments on: Dolly Parton’s boobs have finally caught up with her

item.title: By: Allison
item.dc:creator: Allison
item.description: Dolly has always had big uns. She does the things she does and looks the way she looks because she wants to. Thats how she feels most comfortable. Shes gonna do whatever she wants to do because she has the talent and the dream and the drive. She doesnt give a shit about what people who dont know her think about her and shes not afraid to say it!

item.title: By: Nancy
item.dc:creator: Nancy
item.description: If she'd not had breast augmentation she'd have all my sympathy. I really don't understand who her target audience is. Young men? Doubt it. Older single southern men? Who's buyin' this? Who buys her cds? Maybe people in Mississippi?
